Package: burstMCMC
Title: Inferring transcriptional bursting dynamics from 4sU scRNA-seq data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("David", "Edwards", , "davidedwards.132@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7250-2099"))
Description: Carries out Bayesian inference of transcriptional bursting dynamics parameters from 4sU scRNA-seq data using Markov chain Monte Carlo (Metropolis-adjusted Langevin algorithm (MALA)-within-Gibbs).
